24 subsection (1) or (4) of KRS 189.050, KRS 189.060 to 189.080, subsections (1) to
25 (3) of KRS 189.090, KRS 189.100, 189.110, 189.130 to 189.160, subsections (2) to
26 (4) of KRS 189.190, KRS 189.200, 189.285, subsection (1) or (2) of KRS 189.290,
27 189.300 to 189.338, subsections (1) to (7) and (9) of Section 1 of this Act, KRS
