6 Any person who violates subsection (1)(a) of KRS 189.580 shall be fined not less
7 than twenty dollars ($20) nor more than two thousand dollars ($2,000) or
8 imprisoned in the county jail for not more than one (1) year, or both, unless the
9 accident involved death or serious physical injury and the person knew or should
